theme_override_fonts/normal_font = ExtResource("2_3ypq3")
theme_override_font_sizes/normal_font_size = 14
bbcode_enabled = true
text = "<Translating...>

ATTENTION ALL WARRIOR AND VOIDTROOPER CLASS UNITS: 

UNKNOWN HOSTILE HAS ENTERED OUR VESSEL.

EARLY REPORTS INDICATE HOSTILE IS A MEMBER OF THE DEFILERS WHO INHABITED OUR PROMISED WORLD.

ALTHOUGH IT DOES NOT POSSESS FULL LIKENESS TO ITS RACE, MAKE NO MISTAKE OF ITS ABILITIES AND WEAPONS.


DESTROY IT AT ONCE, LEST OUR JOURNEY TO THIS WORLD BE IN VAIN.



TO ALL ADEPT CLASS UNITS:

OVERSEE YOUR INFERIOR COUNTERPARTS IN THE DEFENSE OF OUR VESSEL. 


DO NOT FEAR, FOR WE HAVE FOUND WHAT WE HAVE SOUGHT, EVEN WITH THE HOSTILES INTERFERENCE.






WE WILL FOLLOW OUR MASTERS CALLINGS.





<End of Transmission>"

