[node name="Label" type="RichTextLabel" parent="TerminalPage3/MarginContainer" unique_id=1613861929]
layout_mode = 2
theme_override_colors/default_color = Color(1, 0, 0, 1)
theme_override_fonts/normal_font = ExtResource("2_3ypq3")
theme_override_font_sizes/normal_font_size = 14
bbcode_enabled = true
text = "<Translating...>

URGENT MESSAGE TO J'YRR PRIME.

THE 12TH BATTLE GROUP HAS DISCOVERED THE SOURCE OF THE SIGNAL WE SET OUT 30 YEARS AGO TO FIND. 


OUR MASTERS HAVE LEFT TECHNOLOGY CAPABLE OF USING A STARS ENERGY TO OPEN A PATH OUTSIDE OF THE UNIVERSE.


THIS EXPLAINS WHY THEY LEFT OUR ANCESTORS OVER 34 MILLION YEARS AGO.


THIS IS HOW WE CONTROL THE UNIVERSE.


GRANDMASTER J'YMA IMPLORES THAT YOU, O EMPEROR, WITNESS THE MOMENT.






MAKE HASTE, AS OTHER RACES HAVE FOUND THE SOURCE OF THE SIGNAL.

WE FOUGHT ONE SUCH, AND THEY HAVE RETALIATED FROM BEYOND THE GRAVE.

THEY HAVE RELEASED A TERRIFYING MACHINE-MAN, THAT ONLY KNOWS WAR.

MAKE HASTE.



<End of Transmission>"

