[node name="Label" type="RichTextLabel" parent="TerminalPage4/MarginContainer" unique_id=210540591]
layout_mode = 2
theme_override_colors/default_color = Color(1, 0, 0, 1)
theme_override_fonts/normal_font = ExtResource("2_3ypq3")
theme_override_font_sizes/normal_font_size = 14
bbcode_enabled = true
text = "<Translating...>

<Message from Grandmaster J'yma>


Understand, Thing... 

I don't know what you are. But you, and whatever bipedal spacefairing race you come from, are defiling my promised world.

When my technicians are finished preparing the Void Bringer, I will personally see you destroyed. 

It is not long until this star will be collapsed. Maybe I'll get the Emperor's authorisation to use it on your homeworld's star too. 



And that AI... Why my fleets didn't destroy your ship when they had the chance I will never understand. Imbeciles. 

That AI, along with you, will be dissassembled, studied by the technicians, then melted down into a heap of slag.

I might get the slag thrown into a star, then collapse the star.

That way you can't respawn from the save terminals.


The Nexyr understand more than you realise. 

How else have we kept our empire running?

You played us for fools, but we have already won.



<End of Transmission>"

